reviewText: If you're looking for wild entertainment, this is not it.  I am very fond of Akira Lane, who appears in this DVD, although her screen time is fairly small.  Overall, it's not bad entertainment but a couple of times I did feel that there was a hint of repetativeness to it.  The girls are all sexy, appealing, and worth the watch, but I would have paid more for a little more screen time from them all.
